Description_lang: Increases the frequency of Maelstrom Weapon being triggered by your melee weapon attacks by $s1%.

description_blz.en_US: Increases the frequency of Maelstrom Weapon being triggered by your melee weapon attacks by 20%.
description_blz.es_MX: Aumenta un 20% la frecuencia con la que tus ataques de arma cuerpo a cuerpo activan Arma vorágine.
description_blz.pt_BR: Aumenta em 20% a frequência com que a Arma da Voragem é ativada pelos seus ataques corpo a corpo.
description_blz.de_DE: Erhöht die Häufigkeit, mit der Eure Waffe des Mahlstroms von Euren Nahkampfangriffen ausgelöst wird um 20%.
description_blz.en_GB: Increases the frequency of Maelstrom Weapon being triggered by your melee weapon attacks by 20%.
description_blz.es_ES: Aumenta un 20% la frecuencia con la que tus ataques de arma cuerpo a cuerpo activan Arma vorágine.
description_blz.fr_FR: Augmente la fréquence du déclenchement d'Arme du Maelström par vos attaques avec des armes de mêlée de 20%.
description_blz.it_IT: Aumenta la frequenza di attivazione dell'Arma del Maelstrom in seguito agli attacchi con l'arma del 20%.
description_blz.ru_RU: Повышает частоту срабатывания "Оружия Водоворота" при попадании атаки ближнего боя на 20%.
description_blz.ko_KR: 근접 공격으로 소용돌이치는 무기 효과가 발동할 확률이 20%만큼 증가합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 使你近戰武器觸發氣漩武器的機率提高20%。
description_blz.zh_CN: 使你的近战武器攻击触发漩涡武器效果的频率提高20%。
